{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":462,"text":"I am a Hazara,"},{"time":2552,"text":"and the homeland\nof my people is Afghanistan."},{"time":7381,"text":"Like hundreds of thousands\nof other Hazara kids,"},{"time":10400,"text":"I was born in exile."},{"time":13164,"text":"The ongoing persecution\nand operation against the Hazaras"},{"time":17366,"text":"forced my parents to leave Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21963,"text":"This persecution has had a long history\ngoing back to the late 1800s,"},{"time":26374,"text":"and the rule of King Abdur Rahman."},{"time":29301,"text":"He killed 63 percent of \nthe Hazara population."},{"time":34897,"text":"He built minarets with their heads."},{"time":37544,"text":"Many Hazaras were sold into slavery,"},{"time":39911,"text":"and many others fled the country\nfor neighboring Iran and Pakistan."},{"time":46204,"text":"My parents also fled to Pakistan,"},{"time":48920,"text":"and settled in Quetta, where I was born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51916,"text":"After the September 11\nattack on the Twin Towers,"},{"time":54857,"text":"I got a chance to go to Afghanistan"},{"time":56645,"text":"for the first time,\nwith foreign journalists."},{"time":59223,"text":"I was only 18, and I got a job\nworking as an interpreter."},{"time":63030,"text":"After four years,"},{"time":65213,"text":"I felt it was safe enough\nto move to Afghanistan permanently,"},{"time":69903,"text":"and I was working there\nas a documentary photographer,"},{"time":74523,"text":"and I worked on many stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78769,"text":"One of the most important\nstories that I did"},{"time":81373,"text":"was the dancing boys of Afghanistan."},{"time":86087,"text":"It is a tragic story about\nan appalling tradition."},{"time":90591,"text":"It involves young kids\ndancing for warlords"},{"time":94052,"text":"and powerful men in the society."},{"time":96141,"text":"These boys are often abducted\nor bought from their poor parents,"},{"time":99902,"text":"and they are put to work as sex slaves."},{"time":102967,"text":"This is Shukur."},{"time":105731,"text":"He was kidnapped from Kabul by a warlord."},{"time":109400,"text":"He was taken to another province,"},{"time":111372,"text":"where he was forced to work as a sex slave\nfor the warlord and his friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116133,"text":"When this story was published\nin the Washington Post,"},{"time":119058,"text":"I started receiving death threats,"},{"time":121380,"text":"and I was forced to leave Afghanistan,"},{"time":125118,"text":"as my parents were."},{"time":127510,"text":"Along with my family,\nI returned back to Quetta."},{"time":131202,"text":"The situation in Quetta had changed\ndramatically since I left in 2005."},{"time":135614,"text":"Once a peaceful haven for the Hazaras,"},{"time":138167,"text":"it had now turned into the most\ndangerous city in Pakistan."},{"time":143601,"text":"Hazaras are confined into two small areas,"},{"time":147176,"text":"and they are marginalized socially,\neducationally, and financially."},{"time":152029,"text":"This is Nadir."},{"time":153469,"text":"I had known him since my childhood."},{"time":155466,"text":"He was injured when his van\nwas ambushed by terrorists in Quetta."},{"time":159645,"text":"He later died of his injuries."},{"time":163221,"text":"Around 1,600 Hazara members"},{"time":167006,"text":"had been killed in various attacks,"},{"time":170629,"text":"and around 3,000 of them were injured,"},{"time":175527,"text":"and many of them permanently disabled."},{"time":178778,"text":"The attacks on the Hazara community\nwould only get worse,"},{"time":182076,"text":"so it was not surprising\nthat many wanted to flee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184908,"text":"After Afghanistan, Iran, Pakistan,"},{"time":189668,"text":"Australia is home to the fourth largest\npopulation of Hazaras in the world."},{"time":196332,"text":"When it came time to leave Pakistan,"},{"time":199141,"text":"Australia seemed the obvious choice."},{"time":201091,"text":"Financially, only one of us could leave,"},{"time":203088,"text":"and it was decided that I would go,"},{"time":204946,"text":"in the hope that if I arrived\nat my destination safely,"},{"time":208299,"text":"I could work to get the rest\nof my family to join me later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213291,"text":"We all knew about the risks,"},{"time":214870,"text":"and how terrifying the journey is,"},{"time":217842,"text":"and I met many people\nwho lost loved ones at sea."},{"time":222416,"text":"It was a desperate decision to take,\nto leave everything behind,"},{"time":226805,"text":"and no one makes this decision easily."},{"time":229680,"text":"If I had been able\nto simply fly to Australia,"},{"time":231866,"text":"it would have taken me\nless than 24 hours."},{"time":234490,"text":"But getting a visa was impossible."},{"time":238576,"text":"My journey was much longer,"},{"time":240689,"text":"much more complicated,"},{"time":242943,"text":"and certainly more dangerous,"},{"time":245989,"text":"traveling to Thailand by air,"},{"time":248631,"text":"and then by road and boat\nto Malaysia and into Indonesia,"},{"time":253429,"text":"paying people and smugglers all the way"},{"time":255844,"text":"and spending a lot of time hiding"},{"time":258584,"text":"and a lot of time in fear of being caught."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262300,"text":"In Indonesia, I joined a group\nof seven asylum seekers."},{"time":266687,"text":"We all shared a bedroom"},{"time":269241,"text":"in a town outside of Jakarta called Bogor."},{"time":273119,"text":"After spending a week in Bogor,"},{"time":275419,"text":"three of my roommates\nleft for the perilous journey,"},{"time":278868,"text":"and we got the news two days later"},{"time":282700,"text":"that a distressed boat sank\nin the sea en route to Christmas Island."},{"time":287506,"text":"We found out that our three roommates --\nNawroz, Jaffar and Shabbir --"},{"time":291267,"text":"were also among those."},{"time":293218,"text":"Only Jaffar was rescued."},{"time":295656,"text":"Shabbir and Nawroz were never seen again."},{"time":299249,"text":"It made me think,"},{"time":300898,"text":"am I doing the right thing?"},{"time":303568,"text":"I concluded I really had\nno other choice but to go on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307515,"text":"A few weeks later, we got the call\nfrom the people smuggler"},{"time":311370,"text":"to alert us that the boat is ready for us\nto commence our sea journey."},{"time":316060,"text":"Taken in the night towards the main vessel"},{"time":318940,"text":"on a motorboat,"},{"time":320588,"text":"we boarded an old fishing boat\nthat was already overloaded."},{"time":325603,"text":"There were 93 of us,"},{"time":327693,"text":"and we were all below deck."},{"time":329666,"text":"No one was allowed up on the top."},{"time":331919,"text":"We all paid 6,000 dollars each"},{"time":335077,"text":"for this part of the trip."},{"time":337166,"text":"The first night and day went smoothly,"},{"time":339395,"text":"but by the second night, \nthe weather turned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342623,"text":"Waves tossed the boat around,\nand the timbers groaned."},{"time":347568,"text":"People below deck were crying,\npraying, recalling their loved ones."},{"time":351910,"text":"They were screaming."},{"time":353652,"text":"It was a terrible moment."},{"time":355811,"text":"It was like a scene from doomsday,"},{"time":359758,"text":"or maybe like one of those scenes\nfrom those Hollywood movies"},{"time":364583,"text":"that shows that everything\nis breaking apart"},{"time":367788,"text":"and the world is just ending."},{"time":370225,"text":"It was happening to us for real."},{"time":372849,"text":"We didn't have any hope."},{"time":377192,"text":"Our boat was floating\nlike a matchbox on the water"},{"time":380720,"text":"without any control."},{"time":382856,"text":"The waves were much higher than our boat,"},{"time":386618,"text":"and the water poured in faster\nthan the motor pumps could take it out."},{"time":392655,"text":"We all lost hope."},{"time":395511,"text":"We thought, this is the end."},{"time":397950,"text":"We were watching our deaths,"},{"time":399876,"text":"and I was documenting it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402268,"text":"The captain told us"},{"time":404219,"text":"that we are not going to make it,"},{"time":406586,"text":"we have to turn back the boat."},{"time":409767,"text":"We went on the deck"},{"time":411834,"text":"and turned our torches on and off"},{"time":414366,"text":"to attract the attention\nof any passing boat."},{"time":419265,"text":"We kept trying to attract their attention\nby waving our life jackets and whistling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426649,"text":"Eventually, we made it to a small island."},{"time":430084,"text":"Our boat crashing onto the rocks,"},{"time":433335,"text":"I slipped into the water"},{"time":435378,"text":"and destroyed my camera,\nwhatever I had documented."},{"time":439025,"text":"But luckily, the memory card survived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444791,"text":"It was a thick forest."},{"time":447206,"text":"We all split up into many groups\nas we argued over what to do next."},{"time":452965,"text":"We were all scared and confused."},{"time":455333,"text":"Then, after spending\nthe night on the beach,"},{"time":458630,"text":"we found a jetty and coconuts."},{"time":461253,"text":"We hailed a boat from a nearby resort,"},{"time":464249,"text":"and then were quickly handed over\nto Indonesian water police."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468498,"text":"At Serang Detention Center,"},{"time":472100,"text":"an immigration officer came\nand furtively strip-searched us."},{"time":477158,"text":"He took our mobile, my $300 cash,"},{"time":480526,"text":"our shoes that we should not\nbe able to escape,"},{"time":483938,"text":"but we kept watching the guards,\nchecking their movements,"},{"time":489999,"text":"and around 4 a.m.\nwhen they sat around a fire,"},{"time":493842,"text":"we removed two glass layers\nfrom an outside facing window"},{"time":497396,"text":"and slipped through."},{"time":498915,"text":"We climbed a tree next to an outer wall\nthat was topped with the shards of glass."},{"time":503744,"text":"We put the pillow on that"},{"time":506043,"text":"and wrapped our forearms with bedsheets"},{"time":509573,"text":"and climbed the wall,"},{"time":511671,"text":"and we ran away with bare feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515418,"text":"I was free,"},{"time":517207,"text":"with an uncertain future,"},{"time":519924,"text":"no money."},{"time":521734,"text":"The only thing I had was the memory card\nwith the pictures and footage."},{"time":528858,"text":"When my documentary was aired\non SBS Dateline,"},{"time":532275,"text":"many of my friends came to know\nabout my situation,"},{"time":534854,"text":"and they tried to help me."},{"time":536710,"text":"They did not allow me to take\nany other boat to risk my life."},{"time":540448,"text":"I also decided to stay in Indonesia\nand process my case through UNHCR,"},{"time":544953,"text":"but I was really afraid\nthat I would end up in Indonesia"},{"time":548807,"text":"for many years doing nothing\nand unable to work,"},{"time":552461,"text":"like every other asylum seeker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555706,"text":"But it had happened to be\na little bit different with me."},{"time":558930,"text":"I was lucky."},{"time":563923,"text":"My contacts worked to expedite\nmy case through UNHCR,"},{"time":568381,"text":"and I got resettled\nin Australia in May 2013."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573119,"text":"Not every asylum seeker is lucky like me."},{"time":577298,"text":"It is really difficult to live a life\nwith an uncertain fate, in limbo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584588,"text":"The issue of asylum seekers in Australia"},{"time":588419,"text":"has been so extremely politicized"},{"time":591137,"text":"that it has lost its human face."},{"time":594271,"text":"The asylum seekers have been demonized\nand then presented to the people."},{"time":600372,"text":"I hope my story and the story\nof other Hazaras"},{"time":604907,"text":"could shed some light to show the people"},{"time":607960,"text":"how these people are suffering\nin their countries of origin,"},{"time":612261,"text":"and how they suffer,"},{"time":616180,"text":"why they risk their lives to seek asylum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620916,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622426,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}